        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Dum in Dei nomine <placeName ref="#places/43" key="#Monasteries">civitate
                            Placencia</placeName> ad <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Curtes #Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/53"
                            >Sancte Resurrectionis Iesu Christi</orgName> domnus gloriosissimus
                            <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21">Berengarius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs> preerat in monasterium ipsum a karissima
                        domna <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/55">Ingelberga</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">inperatrix</rs> constructum esse videtur, intus aecclesia
                        maiore ipsius monasteri in iuditio residerent <persName
                            key="#Witness #Count #Palatine_count" ref="#people/57"
                            >Sigefredus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Palatine_count">comes palatii</rs> et <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        ipsius <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/105">comitis
                            Placentinis</geogName> una cum <persName key="#Witness #Bishops"
                            ref="#people/20">Everardus</persName> ipsius <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/223"><placeName ref="#places/43"
                                >Placentiae</placeName></orgName>, <persName key="#Witness #Bishops"
                                ><name ref="Ildegerius">Ildegerius</name></persName>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1400"><placeName ref="#places/262"
                                >Laudensis</placeName></orgName>, <persName key="#Witness #Bishops"
                                ><name ref="Adelmannus">Adelmannus</name></persName>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1401"><placeName ref="#places/309"
                                >Concordiensis</placeName></orgName> venerabilibus <rs
                            key="#Bishops">episcopis</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Judge"><name
                                ref="Adelgrasus">Aldegrasus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judge"><name ref="Aldebertus"
                            >Aldebertus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Judge"><name
                                ref="Aquilinus">Aquilinus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judge"><name ref="Farimundus"
                            >Farimundus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Judge"><name
                                ref="Stadelpertus">Stadelbertus</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judge"><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudices</rs> idem augusti, <persName key="#Witness #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Ansemundus">Ansemundus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et reliqui; ibique eorum veniens presentia
                            <persName key="#Abbesses"><name ref="Adelberga"
                            >Adelberga</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatissa</rs> eiusdem monasterii una cum <persName
                            key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities"><name ref="Madelbertus"
                                >Madelbertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities">advocato ipsius
                            monasterii</rs> et ostense sunt ibi <rs key="#Cartula">cartule una</rs>,
                        ubi continebatur in ea ab ordine: Â«In Christi nomine, igitur itaque ego in
                        Dei nomine <persName key="#Queen #Salian" ref="#people/242"
                            >Irmengarda</persName> Deo devota filia bone memoriae domni <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/110">Lodoici</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatoris</rs> qui profesa sum vivere <rs
                            key="#Salian">ex natione mea lege Salica</rs>, vobis <persName
                            key="#Abbesses" ref="#people/1618">Scanburgi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatissa</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Natural_landscape #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Ports #Markets #Public_exactions #Churches #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/53">coenobii monasterio Sanctorum Sixti et
                            Fabiani</orgName>, qui fundatum est intra civitate Placentia, quas
                        quondam augusta Angelberga olim imperatrix genitrix mea a fundamentum
                        aedificavit in propriis rebus suis, dono, cedo, confero pro remedium anime
                        meae vel quondam augustorum genitori et genitrix mea, ut dixit, pro remedium
                        anime meae vobis Sconburgae abbatisse vel ad successoribus tuis in perpetuum
                        ad usum et stipendium <rs key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales">monacharum Dei ibique
                            degentium</rs>, qui cotidie in ipsum sanctum et venerabilem locum
                        deserviunt, futuris temporibus eorum iure abendum, hoc est <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >curtes duas iuris meas</rs> qui sunt positas <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Comitatus" ref="#estates/193">in comitatu <placeName
                                ref="#places/191">Regiensis</placeName></geogName>; una ex his in
                        fundo et loco <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/40"><placeName ref="#places/33"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Wardestalla</placeName></geogName> hubi <geogName
                            key="#Houses #Natural_landscape #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Ports #Markets #Public_exactions #Teloneum #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            ref="#estates/194"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/435">Felina</placeName></geogName> dicitur, alia hubi
                            <geogName
                            key="#Houses #Natural_landscape #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Ports #Markets #Public_exactions #Teloneum #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius #Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#estates/38"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/32">Luciaria</placeName></geogName> dicitur cum <rs
                            key="#Churches">capellas duas</rs>, una qui est in honore <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/140">sancti Georgii</orgName>, alia in honore
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/139">sancti Petri</orgName>. Has vero
                        prenominatas curtes cum omnibus earum adiacentiis vel pertinentiis suis <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">de meo iure et
                            dominio transfundo in prenominatum coenobium</rs> ad usum et stipendia
                        monacharum Dei ibique degentium, confirmo abendum futuris temporibus tam <rs
                            key="#Houses">casis</rs> scilicet, <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests"
                            >silvis</rs>, <rs>salectis</rs>, <rs>stationibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>, <rs key="#Natural_landscape">vallibus,
                            ripis, rupinis</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">divisum et
                            indivisum</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">aquis aquarumque decursibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">Bundini atque Ducalis piscationibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">arboribus
                            pomiferis et inpomiferis</rs>, tam <rs key="#Markets #Public_exactions"
                            >mercatas</rs> quamque et <rs key="#Teloneum">toloneum</rs> seu <rs
                            key="#Ports">portoras</rs> in <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio Padi</rs> cum
                        omnia iura et adiacentiis suarum cum <rs key="#Royal_slave">servos et
                            ancillas</rs>, <rs key="#Royal_aldius">aldiones vel aldionas utriusque
                            sexus</rs>, quicquid dici aut nominari potest, omnia ad integritatem a
                            <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/110">genitore meo</persName>
                        aut <persName key="#Queen" ref="#people/55">genitrice mea</persName> sicut
                        fuerunt posesse vel defense et modo a me sunt posesse, nisi tantum
                        anteposita <rs key="#Curtes">curticella una</rs> in comitatu Regisiano in
                        loco qui dicitur <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/77"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Lectora Paludani</placeName></geogName>, cum <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">duobus masariciis</rs> qui pertinere
                        videntur de curte Luciaria, qui regere videtur una per filio <persName><name
                                ref="Bonivertus">Boniverti</name></persName> et alia per
                                <persName><name ref="Albertus/Adelmannus">Alberto</name></persName>
                        de ipso loco, qui Adelmanni dicimus, per cartulam dedi seu et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sortes tres et dimidia</rs> in <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Runcarioli</placeName> qui pertinet de curte
                        Wardestalla, quas <persName key="#Deacons"><name ref="Everardus"
                                >Evrardi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diacono</rs> usufructario dedi diebus vite suae; post
                        eius discessum deveniant in predicto cenobium, ut supra, pro remedium anime
                        meae, nam altera omnia, ut supra, una cum accessione et introitu suarum cum
                        superiora et inferiora suarum cum omnia super astantem vel abentem ex
                        integrum ita abendi, tenendi, possedendi, fruendi et faciendi exinde tam vos
                        quamque et successoribus vestris secundum Deum quod voluerit, ut dixi, pro
                        remedium anime meae et quondam genitori et genitrice mea. Si quis vero, quod
                        in futuris esse non credo, si fuerint in postmodum aut ego ipsa Hirmengarda
                        aut aliquis de eredibus ac proheredibus meis seu quislibet ulla oppositaque
                        persona qui contra hanc cartulis donationis seu cessionis vel offersionis
                        meae, quae pro anima mea fieri et firmare rogavi, venire aut frangere vel
                        emutare voluerit et ad me et ad heredibus meis vobis defensatum non fuerit,
                        tunc tantum et alteris im tantum vobis daturus esse promitto in consimili
                        loco, et insuper <rs key="#Penalty">aurum obtimum libras quinque, argentum
                            ponderas decem</rs> vobis coactum exsolvat, et quod repecierimus et
                        vindicare non valeamus, set presens donationis vel cessio ista omnique
                        tempore firma et inconvulsa permaneat cum stipulatione subnixa. Et taliter
                        iusta et secundum legem meam Salicam, in qua manifesta sum vivere, vobis
                        Sconburge abbatisse ad partem earum monache, que cotidie in iam dicto
                        sanctum et venerabilem locum deserviunt, trado et legitimam faticio
                        investituram ad usum et stipendia habendum <rs key="#Public_rituals">per
                            vuasonem terrae cultellum festucum nodatum frondes arborum </rs>presenti
                        die eorum iure habendum omnia sicut supra legimus; et me exinde foris
                        abvuarpisco et abasasito feci his presentibus, et birgamina cum atramentario
                        de terra levavi et <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Leo"
                            >Leone</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scribere rogavi. Quidem et ego Leo notarius
                        rescribsi pridie kal. Decembr., anno domni <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/82">Witoni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs> tercio, indictione nona. Actum Placentia.
                        Signum manus suprascripte Hermengarde Deo devota qui hanc cartulam fieri et
                        firmare rogavi. Signum manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Fulcus"
                                >Fulconi</name></persName> ex <rs key="#Natio">genere Francorum</rs>
                        testis. Signum manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Albericus"
                                >Alberici</name></persName> [ex] genere Francorum. Signum manus
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Roduinus">Rodoini</name></persName>
                        ex genere Francorum. Signum manus <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Wallaro">Vuallaroni</name></persName> ex genere Francorum
                        testis. Signum manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Radulfus"
                                >Ratulfi</name></persName> ex genere Francorum testis. Ego Leo
                        notarius scriptor huius cartule postradita complevi et dediÂ». Quidem et ego
                            <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni regis ex iussione Sigifredi comiti
                        sacri palacii et amonitione predictorum iudicum scripsi. Anno regni domni
                        Berengarii regi Deo propiciatio XV, mense ianuario, indicione sexta. Signum
                        [manus] suprascripto Sigifredi comiti palatii qui ut supra interfui.
                        Heverardus humilis episcopus interfui et subscripsi. Adalmannus episcopus
                        interfui et subscripsi. Aldegrasus iudex regis interfui. Adelbertus iudex
                        domni regis interfui. Farimundus iudex domni regis interfui.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
